[i]"The game is an absolutely piece of art"[/i]
                                                      [i]Agnus[/i]

[h1]Just a simple review:[/h1]

  [b]PROS:[/b]
[list]
[*]The level of acting is impressive, for a videogame. The actors raised a lot the value of this game;
[*]Editing in this game is very good, the scenes are something that will never stop to attract you to play another time;
[*]The storyline is very impressive. I have no words, I'm still playing over and over;
[*]The fact is a movie, it's an original concept;
[*]There are multiple endings;
[*]Choices must be smart, and also not. Also the smartest choice can be annoying;
[*]There are no wrong options and no gameover (as I've seen);
[*]It's long like a movie.
[/list]
  [b]CONS:[/b]
[list]
[*]Scenes are not skippable the second time you are watching them, so you will get bored watching them again;
[*]You can't save to take another choice in a second moment, also at the end of a story you lose all the progress;
[/list]

Also, remember to not fuck up with the Tchois and their fucking rice pot!
